<p id=3D"p-1806">We compute</p>
<div class=3D"displaymath">
\begin{equation*}
\begin{array}{rll} y' \amp =3D\amp  \ds\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\ds\frac{\Delta y=
}{\Delta t}  \\ \\ \amp =3D\amp \ds\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\ds\frac{(t+\Delta t)=
^2-t^2}{\Delta t} \\ \\ \amp =3D\amp \ds\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\ds\frac{t^2+2t\=
Delta t+\Delta t^2-t^2}{\Delta t} \\ \\ \amp =3D\amp \ds\lim_{\Delta t\to0}=
\ds\frac{2t\Delta t+\Delta t^2}{\Delta t} \\ \\ \amp =3D\amp \ds\lim_{\Delt=
a t\to0} \left(2t+\Delta t\right) =3D 2t. \end{array}
\end{equation*}
</div>
