es/Math%20157%20Course%20Notes/images/image-207.svg" style=3D"width: 100%; =
height: auto;" alt=3D""></div><p id=3D"p-1853-part2"></p></li>
<li id=3D"li-564"><p id=3D"p-1854">The rate of change of \(f\) at \(x =3D 2=
\) is zero.</p></li>
