</div></div></article></div>
<article class=3D"exercise-like" id=3D"exercise-160"><a data-knowl=3D"" cla=
ss=3D"id-ref" data-refid=3D"hk-exercise-160" href=3D"https://www.sfu.ca/mat=
h-coursenotes/Math%20157%20Course%20Notes/sec_TheDerivativeFunction.html"><=
